Package: polyMatrix
Version: 0.1.3
Title: Infrastructure for Manipulation Polynomial Matrices 
Description: 
  A collection of functions to implement classes for polynomial matrix manipulations.
  The package introduces class polyMatrix which allows storing a matrix of polynomials and
  implements basic matrix operations includes a determinant, characteristic polynomial.
  Additionally, it includes basic methods for implementing VARM processes.
